---
---

<section id="features" class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>From idea to reviewed content, without losing control.</h2>
      <p>A practical workflow that turns your creator voice into multi-format drafts you can trust</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Your Voice, Not Generic AI</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">🎯</div>
        </div>
        <p>A short weekly ritual and persona inputs give the system enough context to propose content that sounds closer to you, not a generic chatbot.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>One Idea, Six Formats</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">🔀</div>
        </div>
        <p>Start from one idea and prepare the formats you actually need: blog post, newsletter, social post, short video script, or reel.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Content Built From Search Data</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">📊</div>
        </div>
        <p>Keyword data and competitor analysis inform article direction, so your drafts target real search demand instead of guesswork.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Publishing With Clear Limits</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">🚀</div>
        </div>
        <p>Connect supported social channels when you are ready. ContentFlow keeps account state, review, scheduling, and publish feedback visible in one workspace.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Usable During Short Outages</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">🛠️</div>
        </div>
        <p>When network or API access drops, supported parts of your workspace keep functioning in degraded mode:
          reads use the latest local cache and supported actions are queued for automatic sync
          when the backend is reachable again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Review From Your Phone</h3>
          <div class="feature-icon card-title-icon">📱</div>
        </div>
        <p>The app works on Android, iOS, and web. Review and approve content on the train, in line for coffee, or between meetings. 5 minutes a day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--color-surface-subtle);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: background var(--duration-slow), box-shadow var(--duration-slow), transform var(--duration-slow);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-section {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
</style>
